{
  "stem": "766.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that my mother packed me a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that train, I always, later, when I came for vacation, I did two things on the trains, I ate and slept.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first time, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I went with a girlfriend from my class, which she went also to study, but I'm not so sure.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came to Paris together, and we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took-- they told us where to go, the section for students, and we took a [INAUDIBLE], [? droshka, ?] and we were afraid maybe it would take us somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were-- we were shivering, and the Matura, we were holding here, in-- under the blouse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was the most precious things which we were holding on, and we had whatever the luggage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, he did the-- we thought, who knows where he takes us, but he took us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a horse and buggy, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That time, were no cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we spoke French, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the-- there were no dormitory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Paris, in those times, students lived in hotels in the Quartier Latin, in the Quarter, not because it's the Latin Quarter for amusement, but over there was the medical school and the Sorbonne.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so we-- I don't remember how-- how-- what we told him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went from one little hotel to another to find a room, and they knew that student-- in the beginning, they treated us with suspicion, because in France, you know, a girl had to have a chaperone, and they watched her, and here, are all of a sudden, come two young kids.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Two young kids.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
